name: My Horse Farm: Welcome to Trotterville
My Golf Game featuring Ernie Els
Firearm
description: Firearm was an unreleased game for both the Super NES and Sega Genesis, based on the Malibu Comics multiverse.

name: Tower of the Ancients
description:
A full 360 degrees of puzzle madness - filled with mind-challenging, full colour graphics. Experience the power of the tower with a look-and-feel that will take you away from your mundane life. Challenge your dexterity and your mind with the newest brain bending 3d puzzle game.
Turn the Platform to line up your blocks witch fall from the sky rendered in a beautiful 3d environment. Listen to the surreal music score and become totally immersed in the action. The key to success, mind over matter, speed and persistence.

name: Trainz: Driver Edition
description: Trainz: Driver Edition is a compact version of Trainz Railroad Simulator 2006 where you can have the same driving experience but without the detailed management system.

name: Mystery Masters: Treasures of Mystery Collection
Touch 'N' Play Collection
description: Touch 'N' Play Collection is a collection of 50 casual and classic board games split into four categories: Classic games, arcade, card games and puzzle games.

name: Stream Typers
description: Answer questions in various categories from Twitch chat.

name: Jewel Quest Mysteries IV: The Oracle of Ur
Horror Hotel: Mystery Quest
description: You woke up in an unfamiliar room, enshrouded in darkness. You listen to the silence that's been broken only by the quiet static noise coming from the TV speakers. You try to remember how did you got here. But your memories are gone. You can't get rid of the feeling that something terrible has happened. Writings on the walls. The feeling of being watched. You can hear someone's voice through that static noise... Or is it just your imagination..?

name: The Adventures of Big Faz
description: A 2D Platformer where you must defeat BigWill and return the potatoes to the people

name: Ultimaze
description: Ultimaze is a tile-based puzzle game about navigating small labyrinths.

name: Supershot Golf Robot
description: Supershot Golf Robot is a Sports game, published by Crave, which was cancelled before it was released.

name: The Mirst
description: The Mirst is a horror game, you will be unleashed in front of your house where bizarre events are going to happen to you to find the origin of it all.

name: Sammy Sosa High Heat Baseball 2001: Championship Edition
Tricked N' Tuned: West Coast Streets
The Elder Scrolls: Arena - Deluxe Edition
The Serpent of Isis
description: A Hidden Object Adventure game spanning across Europe, in the search of a lost treasure discovered by your grandfather, which was stolen at some point. It features many varied and interesting levels interspersed with fun (skippable) minigames. The games has a optional feature to turn off time limits to make the game easier. It has a cast of interesting characters, full of mystique.

name: Escape From Lost Island
description: When the fancy cruise ship you’re on starts sinking, it’s a fight to stay alive! Once you manage to get off the sinking cruise ship, you need to survive on an uncharted island! Use your wits to find shelter, avert pirates, escape from the natives, and signal civilization to organize your rescue in Escape from Lost Island. Explore gorgeous Hidden Object scenes and find helpful items that’ll make your journey easier.

name: Lost Lagoon 2: Cursed and Forgotten
description: Escape from a mysterious and dangerous island in Lost Lagoon 2: Cursed & Forgotten! After waking up shipwrecked, you realize that you have been cursed by powers beyond your understanding. Break the curse quickly because malevolent islanders lurk in the lush landscape and are dead set on making you their next victim! Find a way to return home before it's too late.

name: Turn Around Turtle: Show and Tell
The Strangers
description: The Strangers was going to be a one to one fighting game based on characters from Malibu comic books ( plus three new characters made specifically for this game). On EGM issue 59 there is a small preview of the game in a very early state. The Strangers probably was never released because the developer, Malibu Interactive, closed down around 1994 ( the preview is from mid 1994 ).

name: After Egypt
description: After Egypt is a built in game in TempleOS.

name: Ultima Online: Axe Marks the Spot
Tap and Teach: The Story of Noah's Ark
The Fazbear Facility
description: The Fazbear Facility is a FNaF Fangame directed by PhantronGames that is currently in development or has released depending on when you're reading this, all rights to Five Nights at Freddy's belong to Scott Cawthon

name: Threejs
description: Use your arrow keys (← ↑ → ↓) to move. Hold shift to preview.

name: Kofun ha Ikiteiru: Maholova Club no Shitai Sagashi
Uchi no Tenjouura ga Sawagashisugite Shouganai Slowly Neko-hen
Tokyo Coffee Pandechika
description: "Tokyo Coffee Pandechika" is a cafe game that nostalgically depicts the pandemic in Tokyo.

name: Kyua
description: A metafiction RPG set in a real world.

name: Saisen Meikyuu
description: A Japanese-style roguelike that goes through a labyrinth like an Amidakuji.

name: Dappou Undead Factory
description: A dark simulation where you work immortals to make flesh, fight off enemies, and build factories! Events and biohazards may occur...?

name: Pocket Girl: Uketsugareshi Kibou
description: My daughter who was supposed to be dead is right in front of me! Raise your daughter into a lovely lady! Multi-ending nurturing simulation!

name: Shobon no Rukimin! DX: Shobomi to Yuki no Tiara
Project X
description:
Project X is an unreleased spin-off game set in the "bad ending" part of the The Legend of Zelda timeline. It would have explained the origin of the Master Sword and featured Sheik as the main protagonist rather than Link.

The game became known through the concept art being found on the internet through the original artist's web page, which was later taken down. After further research it was discovered that the game was being developed by Retro Studios as a concept, being greenlit by Nintendo to become a prototype, which didn't get approved.

The gameplay seems to have involved an arcade-like whack-a-mole-inspired movement with the Wii Remote to fight against enemies (with wolves being the first ones programmed in the game).

name: Virtomae
description:
A 2000s-style fully customizable virtual pet game!

Take care of your virtual buddy of choice! Have fun together (play an increasing number of minigames, listen to music and watch videos) to make sure they are satisfied! You can also connect with your friends! Return to your pet daily to help it prosper! As presented during the SGDA Summit 2022 Student Games Showcase!

name: Brain Training For Dummies
description: Engage your intellect with 10 fun challenging games to keep your mind fit! Increase your reaction time and improve your memory with great brain building games.

name: Boot Camp Tycoon: Built for Victory
Attack on Tankette
description: A totally new & extremely challenging tank battle game!

name: Fantasy Town
description: Build your vibrant town replete with talented citizens, plant a farm full of prospering crops, or produce valuable goods like milk and eggs on an animal farm! You can also explore the beautiful countryside where surprises abound because limitless adventure and infinite happiness are in store for you in this RPG farming simulation!

name: Block Meister
description: Block grinding pixel art puzzle. Blow up the blocks and make them look like the example.

name: Yumemiru Pyon-pyon Land
description: Yumemiru Pyon-pyon Land is a music/rhythm game.

name: Shuumatsu Shoujo
description: An action game with two girls fighting together to survive the end of the world where crazy people roam.

name: Star Crosser
description: Reclaim the lost light of the 12 constellations! The star guardians use of light wires and high bouncing parries in this 2D action!

name: Chaosground: The Siege for Freedom
description: A new type of "siege party FPS" brought to you by high school students who love FPS. Experience the chaotic war for castle control!

name: LN of Zombies
description: Four warriors try to discover the source of a zombie outbreak in this beat 'em up. Up to 4 players!

name: Angon: The Grim Age
description: In Angon: The Grim Age, strategy faces a medieval apocalyptic world about survival and politics. Enter into the journey that leads the world to chaos and misery, exploring unique places on the wasted land of Eradon. Take decisions that can shape the destiny of the people, battle on turn-based old RPG style and immerse yourself in the rich and deep lore with unique npcs that actually cares with your actions.

name: City Eater
description: Who is the strongest predator? Use various power-up items nearby and eat up the city!

name: Soulvars Fatal Error
description: The soul is the one judging...

name: WonderRun
description: A pixel art run action RPG where you can explore the world of fairy tales, a bit different than the ones we know.

name: Ido
description: Ido is an adventure and an experience that takes you to a mysterious world where you interact with the residents.

name: Haunting Films: Kaiki Film
description: Haunting Films: Kaiki Film is a brain trainer game with a mysterious story and beautiful art.

name: Codename: Apocalypse
description: Codename: Apocalypse is a rogue-like deck-building game that combines role-playing and deck-building elements as one. Play as a normal civilian and try to live as usual, while an unknown doomsday crisis is approaching. Collect various cards to create your own story in the coming apocalypse.

name: Hyakka Girl
description:
Every object on the map can be a weapon or tool!
Show the object to the scholar-chan and register it in the encyclopedia!

name: Akari no Ouji to Kageri no Tou
Chikarou
description: Chikaro is a 2D action game featuring pixel art graphics that incorporate light expressions. The player uses the action of out-of-body experience to explore the field by manipulating enemies and gimmicks.

name: Nature Prhysm
description: A unique freeware rhythm game played on three stacked rows of four buttons. Color divides incoming notes by row and mixes together to mark chords.

name: Kouei no Tou
description: An online 3D shooting game where players divided into 2 teams, "Light" and "Shadow" and buttles 4 vs 4 in max. Players ride on a machine which moves automatically and occupy "Tower" which are placed in stages. It is important for players to get power up items and weapons in the stage.

name: Decimated
description: Decimated is a 3rd person multiplayer online survival RPG. Fight against or team up with other players, scavenge loot, transport cargo or VIPs to other locations, collect legal or illegal resources and trade them, hunt legendary creatures, capture territory and build safehouses for their gang.

name: Build It Green: Back to the Beach
Narin: The Orange Room
description: Narin: The Orange Room is a third-person survival horror game. Play as Narin, a young girl with sixth-sense whose sister mysteriously disappeared. Narin accidentally got involved in the mystical dimension during the twilight time. Find her sister, solve the mystery, and uncover the truth.

name: War on Mars
description: War on Mars is a side-scrolling RTS where you build a powerful army and destroy aliens!

name: Beavis and Butthead Get Big in Hollywood
Choose Your Own Nightmare: The Bite of the Vampire
The Lord of the Rings: Treason of Isengard
description: The Lord of the Rings: The Treason of Isengard was a third-person action-adventure video game for PlayStation 2, Windows, and Xbox. It was the sequel of The Lord of the Rings: The Fellowship of the Ring and like its predecessor was based on the books. It was to be released by Vivendi Universal in late 2003 but was cancelled in September 2003 due to failing the standards Vivendi had set for their games.

name: The Isle of four Winds: Rune War
Quo
description: A first-person dystopian-horror sci fi-liminal adventure inspired by Backrooms. In this mission you are Quo, an autonomous robot explorer. Trace, probe and delve into an unexplored reality full of enigmas and dangers. Now it's your turn.

name: Astraware Casino
description: Try your luck with Astraware Casino - a collection of 12 of the most popular casino games all in one pack. Experience the thrill and enjoy all the fun of a real casino without losing your shirt!

name: The Mystery of the Mary Celeste
Through Time
description: Through Time is a single-player platform game in which you have to pass levels. The more levels you go, the more difficulty increases. Every month there is a new season with a new theme that is illustrated through the levels. You can unlock new characters and play with them, there are also temporary events in which you can unlock a lot of rewards.

name: TKKG: Mystery of the Mayan Treasure
Tiny Toon Adventures: Defenders of the Universe
description:
Tiny Toon Adventures: Defenders of the Universe is a cancelled fighting game based on the Tiny Toon Adventures franchise. It was initially scheduled for release in mid-2002, but was cancelled for unknown reasons, despite having completed development. It was developed by Treasure and originally slated for the PlayStation 2.

On 25 February 2009, a ROM image of the game was released by a member of the Internet forum Lost Levels.

name: The Adventures of Pinocchio: Activity Center
The Adventures of Peter Rabbit & Benjamin Bunny
The Adventures of Busy Billy
description: The Adventures of Busy Billy is a puzzle game aimed at children between 3 and 8. Players choose between two mechanically identical scenarios after starting the game: Busy Billy Wonderland and Busy Billy Fantasy.

name: Aces: The Complete Collector's Edition
description:
This compilation features all flight simulations developed by Dynamix in the early 1990's on one CD-ROM:
- A-10 Tank Killer
- Aces of the Pacific
- Aces Over Europe
- Red Baron

name: The Kings of the Dark Age
Hell-Hell
description: Hell Hell is a cooperative action stealth game that combines "tag" and "hide-and-seek. Players must work together to collect items in the stage as ordered, summon gates and escape from prison within a time limit, while hiding or running away to avoid detection by the demon that roam the stage.

name: Suzu to Mari no Bouken 2: Lost Colors and Golden Bells
Souen no Iseki
description: An adventure game in which you have the solve mysteries while talking with a friend.

name: Frozen
description: Join your favourite Frozen friends, Anna, Elsa, Olaf, Kristoff, Marshmallow and Sven on their adventures through Arendelle and the story of Frozen, help Anna learn to skate, dodge snowballs with Kristoff or learn rhythm with Elsa. Play through the 5 fun, interactive games, unlock enchanting globes in the snow globe gallery, explore the 5 snowflake activities or read the fun e-book collecting magical snowflakes along the way. Teaches vocabulary, spelling, memory, rhythm and beat, problem solving and reading.

name: Cyclopvania
description: Ceyclopvania is an exciting classic Metroivanaia game with a retro pixel look. Experience the journey of a little cyclops out for revenge! Once Odysseus destroyed his grandfather's eye. Now his descendants rule the ophthalmologist lobby, controlling the destiny of the turbo capitalist SteamPunk world. Proletarians and Cyclops unite!

name: Car Go Fast
description: Car Go Fast HD is the HD remaster of the hit game "Car Go Fast" that was made for LD48. This version of the game has upgraded visuals, gameplay, and music.

name: AMF Bowling
description: After the real lanes are closed, where can you go to score that perfect 300? Lighter than a real bowling ball and more portable than a real bowling lane, AMF Bowling is where it's at baby!

name: The Gigglebone Gang: The AlphaBonk Farm
Alien Front
description: Cancelled Port of "Alien Front Online" for the N-Gage. Originally announced by Sega in 2004, a prototype ROM image of the N-Gage version was leaked online in 2019.

name: Hyenas
description:
Hyenas is a hero-based, multiplayer extraction shooter. Choose a Hyena to play as - each with a unique weapon, ability, and personality - to form a crew of three and steal valuable Merch. The action takes place on vast, themed 'Plunderships' returning to Mars from Earth, loaded with salvaged Merch for your crew to steal.

Competing with four other raiding crews, your goal is to find and crack secured vaults, then steal enough Merch to make your escape. Standing in your way are not only rival players but also the “MURFs” – security forces who will fight to the death to protect the precious cargo.

Once a team has stolen enough Merch, they activate the Plundership’s VIP Extraction, which is revealed on the map. You must find it and make your getaway or stop others from making theirs. The crew that escapes first is the winner, so make sure it’s you!

Fast and frenetic combat is enhanced by the unique weaponry and ability of each Hyena. Additionally, each Plundership features zero gravity areas, some of which can be toggled on and off. Gunfights take on an entirely new dimension, literally, when gravity is no longer a concern. Enemy players can come at you from any direction, so you’ll need to keep your head on a swivel – or make sure to ambush them first.

name: A.I. Puzzler
description:
Microsoft A.I. Puzzler was a game being developed by Alexey Pajitnov of Tetris fame, and who previously worked on Microsoft Entertainment Pack: The Puzzle Collection.

It's official website has at least two snapshots on the Wayback Machine dating from July 28th 2001 to August 1st 2001, with its first inaccessability date being August 9th 2001, which meant that the game was shelved between the August 1st and 9th timeframe. It also used to be mentioned on Wikipedia's List of video games published by Microsoft page with the earliest dated from June 15th 2011 and the latest prior to removal being being October 12th 2020.

All that remains is just a scan of the manual.

name: Trainz: The Complete Collection
description: Trainz: The Complete Collection includes: Trainz Railroad Simulator 2004 and 2006, Trainz Routes Volume 1-4 (DLCs), the Ultimate Trainz Collection (an updated version of Trainz) + the Trainz Paint Shed DLC.

name: Tri-Peaks 2: Quest for the Ruby Ring
Tribes Extreme
description: Tribes Extreme is a cancelled Starsiege: Tribes single + multiplayer expansion that was in development for PC by Dynamix, around 1999. It was meant to offer a proper single player experience, with 12 campaign missions and a new tribe featured in the storyline.

name: Hello Kitty: A Day with Hello Kitty and Friends!
description: Come spend a day with Hello Kitty and her friends in this new educational software title for VTech's InnoTab systems. But it's not just any day - it's Hello Kitty's birthday. Read the e-book "Hello Kitty's Surprise" to find out how Hello Kitty spent her birthday, or join in the celebration and play one of three party-themed, touch-screen learning games. You can also make a Hello Kitty greeting card or import your own photos into a digital Hello Kitty photo album in the two creative activities. As your child plays with Hello Kitty on their InnoTab, they'll develop essential skills in counting, addition, logic and memorization.

name: Val d'Isère Ski Park Manager: Gold Edition
Pardon My French Toast
description:
In Pardon My French Toast, you play as a Toasty (a talking slice of brioche) who dreams of participating in the new edition of the bread wrestling competition. To be physically up to the challenge, he decides to follow a training program organized by the previous champion of the discipline, which will take him all over the world and make him meet a bunch of wacky weirdos.

Pardon My French Toast is an adventure / platform game in 2D top view in which the player explores different worlds, solves puzzles and meets a whole bunch of fun characters. Bread wrestling is a... special sport. We will introduce the discipline later.

name: Sesame Street Create & Draw in Elmo's world
House of Necrosis
description:
House of Necrosis is a Mystery Dungeon-style game inspired by Survival Horror and RPG classics of the 32bit era.

Survive the horrors of the mansion that changes every time you enter.

name: Late Night Gas Station
description: Relax as you work a cold, rainy night shift at a gas station. Order stock & gas, stack the shelves and serve your customers! Keep your store well stocked and clean to keep your customers satisfied. Keep entertained and spend your juicy profits on the gas station PC.

name: Twistingo
description: The new Twistingo is a relaxing, revolutionary game that crosses the popular hidden object, classic bingo and the much-loved marble-matching games. The result is fabulous fun that you and your family will enjoy for hours, days, weeks, or a lifetime.

name: 3-D Ultra Radio Control Racers Deluxe: Traxxas Edition
Backstage Pass: The Ultimate Rock and Roll Trivia Game
Win a Million: The Ultimate Quiz Game
World Championship Games: A Track & Field Event
Microsoft Flight Simulator 2000: World Airliners - 747-400 and 777-200 Professional
Fufufu
description: Have you ever raced with sheeps, poked noses, or battled against pirate cats? Welcome to FUFUFU, an adorable roguelite adventure for all ages, full of wacky situations. Get ready for some Fu-lish action!

name: Escape If You Can
description: Quick and easy, little game. You have to escape in a given time and for this you have to find and switch switches and get over for example poisonous liquid and drops. Impediments can decrease your health and kill you. Mixture of a maze game and the first level is a little bit of platformer game.

name: Crimson Standard
description: Crimson Standard is a story-rich adventure RPG game, featuring turn-based combat and flexible character building. Follow the path of Wang Zi who accidentally traveled to an alternative China with magic, exploring the mysteries around the world, and eventually facing the hidden enemy of mankind!

name: Boulder Island
description: The game is a first-person survival battle game, which requires players to defeat the enemy in the game through operation and collection.

name: God-Machine: Shogun CyberMetal Arena
description: Prepare for a mix of endurance-combat and arcade shooting game. Play against dangerous robots, cyborgs, and mutants, in rogue-like arenas that evolves as you fight. Are you brave and skilled enough to endure?

name: FunBall 3D
description: FunBall 3D is a casual game, that involves platforming and collecting score, and if you are not doing that you are racing against the clock, Funball will travel around different maps and challenges.

name: Cyber Drift
description: Welcome to the world of Cyber, hold your steering wheel for the next drift track.

name: Voidwalkers: The Gates of Hell - The Devil's Towers
description: Enter a new hell scape and launch an assault on The Devil's Towers! You and three of your allies must defend three weapon emplacements, while attempting to breach the nine towers that defend a Hive.

name: A Lil' Horror Story: The Camp Fire
description: You got a voucher for a free camping trip, sponsored by The Bank!! YAY!! Time to enjoy the nice outdoors... Good thing boogeymen and monsters don't exist... Heh... Do they?... Collect 12 logs to get through the night...Camp fires are safe... Crouch to be silent...Your Flashlight attracts them...

name: Zombie Maze
description: 'Zombie Maze' is simple top-down shooter game with maze. You need to find way to escape. Only way to escape is helicopter on the roof!! Run!!! and kill those zombies!!!

name: 3D Bowling USA
description: 3-D Bowling USA provides 12 bowlers, five bowling alleys, multiple camera angles, varying techniques, and different lane conditions. Multiplayer options include head-to-head competition and computer opponents.

name: You Don't Know Jack: The Irreverent Collection
Asym Altered Axis
description: Asym Altered Axis is an Asymmetric Multiplayer Game where one player sets the deadly stage with a variety of traps and hunt down the puny fleeing infiltrators, while the other (up to 5) players team up and stealthily pull off the heist under cover of darkness.

name: Shyftrs
description: Shyftrs is a 2D stylized action adventure metroidvania game that will take you on a journey to uncover the mysteries of your lineage and the world beyond. Your weapon of choice are Cane Sword, Pistol or use your new found prowess. Step up and embrace the adventure.

name: Disastory
description: An illustrated choice-driven roleplaying adventure where coffee machines find love and teenage girls steal eyeballs!? Explore a vibrant world with absurd stories and characters.

name: Name That Tune: Country & Western Hits
description: A cartridge expansion for Tiger's Name that Tune handheld.

name: Name That Tune: Music Cartridge
description: A cartridge expansion for Tiger's Name That Tune handheld.

name: The Western Rooms
description: Will you beat the Rooms? None of them will be easy. Challenge your mind with 3 Escape Room Scenarios! Look for clues, and keep your eyes wide open! Explore an old Western Town Find the Bartender's Recipe Break in the Bank's Vault & Escape the Sheriff's Department

name: Fantasy Zoo
description: Fantasy Zoo is a zoo builder where you build zoo for fantasy animals in fantasy world.

name: Dog Adventure Harmony
description: A fictitious RPG where you search for your lost dog in a fantasy world. Fight make-believe monsters and dodge creative bullet hell attacks. Meet its imaginary characters... and their creator if you'd like.

name: Armored Battalion
description: Armored battalion is a overlooking shooting game, which is different from the current tank battle mode. It is more inclined to the arcade. There are two battle modes: the battle mode. You can only use tanks that have fought in history. RPG mode. You can choose chassis and artillery freely.

name: Home Sick
description: This is a horror puzzle game. To be a successful player, use objects in the mystery house wisely, and find the meaning of this metaphoric story.

name: Independence Day
description: Laser gun version of Independence Day by Tiger Electronics.

name: Hidden
description: A new way to play the classic Hide and Seek game. Explore a big mansion divided in 4 biomes and full of traps. Play as a Hunter and find out all your targets or hide everywhere in the role of a "Hidden". Use your ability, team up with other players and reach the victory.

name: Nuclear Fighter
description: Is a fun and fast 2D platformer with a side view. Your goal is to escape from the city and survive.

name: Toy's Paradise
description: Wake up a toy ready to tear the world apart! Move around the house, trying to tear everything down in a way to gain resources. Use these resources to build more toys, as well as other tools to increase efficiency in pulling this poor family's house apart.

name: Skip Lake 2
description: “Solve beautiful puzzles and listen to the melody of crashing Pots going deeper into the story of Skip Lake!”

name: SynthWaves
description: A retrowave tower defense game where the player must manage their arsenal of sentries to fight off waves of synths, stop their invasion, and take the fight to their home.

name: Updog
description: Updog is a game all about getting that dog up. Jump, dive, grapple, and ground pound your way across the cloudscape to grab balloons and fuel for your raft, your one ticket to the heavens.

name: Night Janitor
description: A first-person horror game where you clean up after rowdy high school kids while also keeping a lookout for clues as to their disappearance. Scrub, vacuum, clean... die?

name: The Original Wizard
description: The game is a Dungeon Crawler, where the player must survive the succeeding dungeons and defeat Impeficus on his throne.

name: An Ace Walks Into a Bar
description: Maya is lured away from a cozy night in with her girlfriend by the offer of a "girls' night out" with her older sister Lynn. Unfortunately for Maya, this family reunion doesn't go as well as she hoped...

name: Punirunzu
description:
A pet simulator with jelly pets that you can touch. They evolve depending on what jelly you choose to use. There are many tasks that can be done and also mini-games to get money to buy food for your puni pet.
The game is made by Takara tomy

name: Kingdom Under Fire: Avalanche
description:
Kingdom Under Fire Avalanche was a online game that will allow players to battle each other as 2 heroes from the other Kingdom Under Fire Series. It will also have a PvE mode where players have a AI army and they must defeat the other AI army.

It was supposed to be realesed in 2017. The game was shown in beta in 2011 in Korea but due to poor reviews it ended up being cancelled.

name: Extracurricular Activities
description: Extracurricular Activities is a visual novel following the main character (you!) through his endeavor of trying to romance a member of his tennis team. The choices you make can impact the way your teammates react to you, so make your choices carefully.

name: Doggy
description:
You play as a red Box and for you to survive the game you have to reach the end of the platform without touching any of the grey barriers.
Good Luck and i will see you in the end.

name: Cosmic Strike: The Last Sub Sector
description: Giant capital ship combat! Equip your crew, choose your ship and rage battle across the stars in this top down 2D strategic shooter. Unravel the story as you fight hordes of enemies, build up your base, and become the fleet commander this sector needs in its darkest hour.

name: The Fairyland Story
description: An NES/Famicom prototype of arcade game The Fairyland Story. It was never released.

name: Fascination
description: Fascination is an unreleased erotic arcade game developed by Nintendo in 1974 using the Laser Clay Shooting System.

name: Bob Ross: The Joy of Painting
description: Enjoy making happy little trees with this, the game based on Bob Ross' television paint show, The Joy of Painting.

name: Piano Keys
description: Beautifully in tune, Piano Keys has even more songs in its repertoire! Its sharply lit, stand-out-in-the-crowd cabinet and marquee are sure to entertain the entire audience!

name: Dead or Alive: Code Chronos
description: Dead or Alive: Code Chronos is a cancelled game from the Dead or Alive series. During a interview with Play Magazine in July, 2006, Tomonobu Itagaki stated that Code Chronos would be a prequel to the Dead or Alive series, and would relay the story of Ayane and Kasumi before the first tournament.

name: Blob Dash
description: Jump, dash and reverse time to avoid obstacles and achieve a high score.

name: Monsters University: Hide and Sneak
description: Even monsters have to go to school! And so does the crew from Disney’s Monsters University. Help Mike practice for the Scare Games by navigating the obstacle course set in the frat house and scoring a perfect scare!

name: In-Flight Pac-Man
description: Help Pac-Man make his way through the maze and munch the dots and prizes. In order to survive a few rounds, avoid the pesky ghosts or you’ll be game over soon!

name: Disney's Classic Games
description: Disney Classic Games is another great way for kids to learn the alphabet and colours. Donald Duck and his friends have 3 different cool activities for kids. Make them feel that learning can also be fun.

name: Royal Dungeon
description: The king and his queen are trapped in their castle which suddenly turned out as a very dangerous place. The goal is to escape those two from the deadly castle, helping them to avoid a variety of enemies and traps.

name: Burgal's Bounty
description: Join the heist! Help Burgal steal money to save his girlfriend, Burgette, from the mob. Direct him through each treacherous puzzle by placing arrows to guide him! Set bombs to blow up obstacles in his way! Defeat epic bosses! Collect money bags to complete each puzzle, coins to unlock extra secret puzzles, and diamonds to buy new costumes!

name: The Quest Classic: Asteroids
description:
The Quest Classic: Escape from Asteroids is an expansion to The Quest Classic, a beautifully hand-drawn, immersive and enchanting world full of exciting challenges.
After enabling the expansion, you can continue to play The Quest Classic with your existing character(s) to explore new areas and quests. However, if you don't have The Quest Classic, you can also play the expansion as a standalone game.
Your ship has run off course, Hero. You find yourself sucked into a black hole that warps you far away. The world you know so well is gone. It's as though there were a huge explosion. All around you the asteroids appear on fire. You feel great pain and pass out . You wake up in a strange room with an unearthly creature looking down on you.

name: The Quest: Hero of Lukomorye IV
description:
The Quest: Hero of Lukomorye IV is an expansion to The Quest, a beautifully hand-drawn open world role playing game with old school grid-based movement and turn based combat.
After enabling the expansion, you can explore new areas and adventures. However, if you don't have The Quest, you can also play the expansion as a standalone game.
Grab your weapons and spells! The war is over but Kozney the Deathless refuses to give up his chance for the throne. While winter chokes Lukomorye in its icy grip, Kozney has summoned strong forces to defeat the Tzar's loyal army and navy. It's time to face the Deathless once again. This time it must be Death to the Deathless!
To access the new areas (not applicable if you are playing the expansion standalone), go to Mithria harbor and talk to captain Hanty, then select "Luko IV" as your travel destination. It's recommended you reach at least level 70 before taking on the challenges posed by this expansion.

name: The Lord of the Tower
description: Once upon a time, there lived an amiable folk in the small kingdom of Ukron, ruled by a responsive and fair king. But the hard times came to the kingdom. A dark army under the command of Pukin invaded the peaceful lands and enslaved all their populace, having deceived the people with a sweet honeycake. But not everyone submitted the invader. A brave volunteer corps gathered together and rebuffed the impure force. Help the soldiers build protective structures, defend your king and the whole kingdom of Ukron.

name: Nova Battles
description:
Competitive ability, awareness and teamwork are just some of the skills needed to succeed at NovaBattles! Through our 3v3 game modes, players are pushed to the limits in mobile gaming, making sure that talent really does pay. At the same time, through cleverly designed mechanics, a two-tiered currency in place. An in-game gold coin can be used to buy a number of collectables, including our super Heroes!

NovaBattles presents to you a free, PVP, multiplayer online battle arena (MOBA) suitable for players of all types and ages! No matter if you’re a casual gamer, or a seasoned professional - there’s something for everyone!

name: Going Into the Unknown
description: After a girl is infected with an epidemic and the townspeople are infected, you have to face and kill enemies or hide from them, solve puzzles and find documents to complete missions.

name: Polyemisokos
description: An abstract puzzle game about connections.

name: Trainz Plus: CP SD40-2 #5865-5879 Dual Flags
description: Drive the CP GMD SD40-2 locomotive, numbers 5865-5879, built in 1984 for CP Rail. Featuring many exact details found on the real locomotives, including CP specific cooling pipe, Locotrol antenna array, open bearung EMD HTC trucks, and more!

name: Trainz Plus: Lone Pine Branch
description: A rural and largely single track connection between UP and BNSF owned main lines.

name: Trainz Plus: PREG B16mnopux 087
description: Used for regional passenger trains in Poland, Romania, Czech Republic, and Germany this passenger coach features photorealistic fully PBR textures, and many different options.

name: Trainz Plus: DR DBmtrue 215
description: Carry passengers around your routes with these highly detailed European passenger coaches!

name: Trainz Plus: NS SD60E - 6963 GoRail
description: Norfolk Southern SD60E in the special NS GORAIL livery. Features include Brand new Custom Cab and in-cab Signals, Fan Animation, Ditch Lights, and more!

name: Trainz Plus: TE3-2068
description: The legendary TE3 locomotive is made in compliance with the highest standards for quality and precision. This is a replica of a locomotive TE3 series.

name: Trainz Plus: ECML Edinburgh - Dundee
description: This well known route based in 1976 includes the Forth and Tay rail bridges and the stunning scenery along the Firth of Forth estuary.

name: Trainz Plus: Mine & Field railway
description: A small module showcasing a set of content designed for representing underground mining scenes and particularly the underground transport of coal and other ores plus mining equipment and personnel. Includes mining locomotives and rolling stock, and a range of infrastructure.

name: Trainz Plus: Amtrak F40PH 2 pack
description: Amtrak F40PH locomotive two pack, with Phase II and Phase III liveries. Feature full custom cab, automatic running numbers, animated wipers, gecko script, and more.

name: Trainz Plus: DBuz 747 Passenger Cars
description: The cars are still to be found on Germany’s railways today. They are the backbone of local traffic: the famous double-deck car, affectionately known as ‘Dostos’ for short.

name: Trainz Plus: PRR X23 Boxcar
description: Experience the trendsetting X23boxcar in firstclass quality from 3DZUG and let the past come alive again.

name: Trainz Plus: Healesville 1910's
description: This layout covers the last 19 miles of the Healesville line from Mooroolbark to Healesville, set in approximately 1913-1920, prior to the line to Lilydale being electrified, and during the period when the locomotives were painted Canadian Red.

name: Trainz Plus: Season Town Northern Rail Road Route
description: A fictional route situated in the USA. The route reacts to season changes and lets you drive a freight train on the main line as well as a street car through the city.

name: Trainz Plus: PREG B16mnopux 039
description: Carry passengers around your routes with these highly detailed European passenger coaches!

name: Trainz Plus: RZD-UZ-RIC Wagons Praha
description: The RIC and UZ passenger wagons are made in compliance with the highest quality standards and precision.

name: Trainz Plus: CO17-3373
description: A series of freight locomotives CO (Sergo Ordzhonikidze, axle load 17 tonnes) designed for medium loads and working on lines with light rail. Built from 1934 to 1951 at the Kharkov, Bryansk, Voroshilovgrad, Krasnoyarsk and Ulan-Ude Locomotive Works. Total production of locomotives - 3049.

name: Trainz Plus: Florida Rail Road Museum Model Railroad
description: Based upon the model railroad in UP coach 5642 at the Florida Railroad Museum, this layout is scaled to HO scale and offers multiple industries and a circus!

name: Trainz Plus: Inzer - South Ural Mountains
description: A beautiful replica of the railways of central Eurasia, in the Ural mountain range.

name: Trainz Plus: Halloween Night on Kickstarter County
description: Its Halloween night on Kickstarter County and you are taking the last coal train from Daydream Mine to the yard located in St. Nicolaas before heading off for the night. What is supposed to be a simple run turns into a spooky experience…

name: Trainz Plus: Shortline Railroad
description: A fictional route in the USA where the Burlington Northern railroad uses GP38-2 locos to help serve the industries that rely on the railroad for their main source of transportation and for local runs on the main line. Welcome to the Shortline Railroad!

name: Trainz Plus: Pro Train - Class 68 TPN
description: Drive the modern TransPenning Express livery Class 68 diesel-electric locomotive!

name: Trainz Plus: BNSF GE Dash-9 44CW Warbonnet
description: Jump straight in and drive the BNSF GE Dash-9 44CW Warbonnet in 'easy' or 'realistic' mode.

name: Trainz Plus: Avery - Drexel Route
description: Discover the winding tracks through the iconic snowy hills of the famous North American freight and passenger route.

name: Trainz Plus: Amtrak P42DC - Phase III
description: Amtrak P42DC locomotive in Phase III livery. Feature full custom cab, automatic running numbers, animated wipers, gecko script, and more.

name: Trainz Plus: Chesapeake & Ohio K3-K3a 2-8-2
description: Drive the Chesapeake & Ohio's K-3 and K-3a Mikado locomotives. With 63inch drivers, 28in by 32in cylinders, and a 200PSI boiler, the K-3 and K-3a locomotives exerted 67,698pounds of tractive effort, providing plenty of power to haul goods trains.

name: Trainz Plus: Industrial Switching
description: Somewhere in Canada, in the city of Longview, offers a challenging industrial park that will challenge the train crews critical thinking skills to navigate and properly spot the freight cars. Industrial Switching is an industrial themed route servicing 15 industries.

name: Trainz Plus: Cilie Oldphartz Railroad
description: The Cilie Oldphartz Railroad Company is a TRS19 model railroad style route that comes in three variants - a narrow gauge logging railroad, a narrow gauge mining railroad and a standard gauge railroad. Each has the same track layout, with variations to suit the gauge and theme.

name: Trainz Plus: Trainz Route - Rostovsky Uzel
description: The route is based on a real section of the North Caucasian railway, located in the Rostov region of the Russian Federation.

name: Trainz Plus: Pro Train - Class 68 Chiltern Railways
description: Drive the modern TransPenning Express livery Class 68 diesel-electric locomotive!

name: Trainz Plus: GT GP9
description: The 2 pack comes with the GT GP9 Black and Blue livery. The session lets you jump straight in and drive the GT GP9 using 'easy' or 'realistic' mode.

name: Trainz Plus: RZD-UZ-RIC Wagons
description: The RIC and UZ passenger wagons are made in compliance with the highest quality standards and precision. Photo realistic textures and geometry has been recreated as accurately as possible to deliver the characteristics and details of the original wagons.

name: Trainz Plus: DB DBmu748 080
description: Carry passengers around your routes with this highly detailed European passenger coach!

name: Trainz Plus: ATSF GP38-2 Santa FE
description: Climb on board your new GP38-2 ATSF engines and learn to operate the EMD GP38-2 ATSF locomotive. This detailed session will make you an expert Train driver and best of all, you get to experience it all driving the beautifully detailed GP38-2 ATSF

name: Trainz Plus: Andrushivka - Vinnitsa UZ
description: East European railway. The route runs along the vast expanses of the Ukraine among the picturesque fields, forests and villages.

name: Trainz Plus: Tidewater Point Railroad 2.0
description: Tidewater Railroad is a shortline railroad running from a crude oil terminal located south by the river to an intermodal terminal in the North.

name: Trainz Plus: Balezino Mosti Sessions - Lichachove to Mosti
description: This pack includes two sessions for the separate Balezino - Mosti, Russia, operating a passenger train from Lichachove to Mosti during the day, and during the night. Note, this pack requires the separate Balezino - Mosti, Russia route.

name: Trainz Plus: RVSX Vegetation Control Train
description: Complete vegetation control train. SW1500, Tool Car, Crew/Dorm, Chemical Cars, Scripted Weed Control Car with animated spraying arms that you can control. The sprayer car is scripted and animated, controlled via the 'view details' window.

name: Trainz Plus: PolRegio B16mnopux 035
description: Used for regional passenger trains in Poland, Romania, Czech Republic, and Germany this passenger coach features photorealistic textures, fully PBR textures, and many different options.

name: Trainz Plus: JR Rolling Stock Pack
description: This package is bursting with Jointed Rail rolling stock all ready for you to drive in TRS19!

name: Trainz Plus: Chesapeake & Ohio K2 2-8-2
description: The Class K2 had 63 diameter drivers, 28 x 30 cylinders, had a 200 psi boiler pressure and exerted 63,467 pounds. The Class K-2 firebox was 287 square feet. The evaporative heating surface was 4,160 square feet and with the superheater the combined heating surface was 5,333 square feet.

name: Trainz Plus: British Rail Class 70 - Colas Rail
description: Drive the highly detailed, modern British GE Class 70 in Colas Rail livery in Trainz. Developed by 3DZUG for TRS19 using the latest PBR technologies, and many custom features!

name: Trainz Plus: CO17-1374
description: A series of freight locomotives CO (Sergo Ordzhonikidze, axle load 17 tonnes) designed for medium loads and working on lines with light rail. Built from 1934 to 1951 at the Kharkov, Bryansk, Voroshilovgrad, Krasnoyarsk and Ulan-Ude Locomotive Works. Total production of locomotives - 3049.

name: Trainz Plus: Niddertalbahn
description: An idyllic, single-track branch line in Wetterau and Main-Kinzig-Kreis in the western German state of Hesse.

name: Trainz Plus: Balezino Mosti
description: A route in the extent of 57 km between Balezino and Mosti, Russia. Beautifully detailed landscapes and an electrified railway connect these two cities.

name: Trainz Plus: Cornish Mainline and Branches
description: This picturesque route runs between Truro and terminates in Penzance and includes Branch-lines to Falmouth (The Maritime Route), Helston, Hayle Wharves and St Ives.

name: Trainz Plus: ITC GP7 Phase I & II
description: This pack allows you to jump in and drive the ITC GP7 Phase I and II locomotives in your own sessions. Find them under the Trains Tab by searching for 'ITC' in Surveyor.

name: Trainz Plus: CO17-1471
description: A series of freight locomotives CO (Sergo Ordzhonikidze, axle load 17 tonnes) designed for medium loads and working on lines with light rail. Built from 1934 to 1951 at the Kharkov, Bryansk, Voroshilovgrad, Krasnoyarsk and Ulan-Ude Locomotive Works. Total production of locomotives - 3049.

name: Trainz Plus: CO17-4171
description: A series of freight locomotives CO (Sergo Ordzhonikidze, axle load 17 tonnes) designed for medium loads and working on lines with light rail. Built from 1934 to 1951 at the Kharkov, Bryansk, Voroshilovgrad, Krasnoyarsk and Ulan-Ude Locomotive Works. Total production of locomotives - 3049.

name: Trainz Plus: NS SD60E - Horsehead
description: Norfolk Southern SD60E in the standard NS 'Horsehead' livery. Features include Brand new Custom Cab and in-cab Signals, Fan Animation, Ditch Lights, and more!

name: Trainz Plus: Shmmns Coil Transporter
description: Get on board and extend your vehicle fleet with this highly detailed Shmmns-Coilwagon. Two sessions for the free Niddertalbahn route are included in this package.

name: Trainz Plus: PREG Bmnopux 003
description: Used for regional passenger trains in Poland, Romania, Czech Republic, and Germany this passenger coach features photorealistic fully PBR textures, and many different options.

name: Trainz Plus: CONTZ Pack - Basic Edition
description: The Contz Pack Basic Edition featurees a set of 20ft and 40ft dry van shipping containers in a variety of paint schemes, along with three versions of the X2K double stack container well wagons.

name: Trainz Plus: Chiyoda Branch Line
description: The Chiyoda Branch Line is the Tokyo Metro Line in Tokyo, Japan. This route will bring you the landscape of Japan's suburban city.

name: Trainz Plus: CO17-1171
description: A series of freight locomotives CO (Sergo Ordzhonikidze, axle load 17 tonnes) designed for medium loads and working on lines with light rail. Built from 1934 to 1951 at the Kharkov, Bryansk, Voroshilovgrad, Krasnoyarsk and Ulan-Ude Locomotive Works. Total production of locomotives - 3049.

name: Trainz Plus: ECML Kings Cross - Edinburgh 1976
description: This route covers the full route from London Kings Cross Station all the way to Edinburgh in Scotland - a 393 mile drive! With significant updates to almost every feature along the track, the route will take you back in time to 1976 UK.
